                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Aelia Hygia vixit <lb n="3"/>annis XVIII <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Ael</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Valent<supplied reason="lost">inus</supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>col</abbr><ex>oniae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Apul</abbr><ex>ensis</ex></expan><certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> <expan><abbr>fl</abbr><ex>amen</ex></expan><certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> <lb n="6"/>libertae et coniugi <lb n="7"/>gratae <lb n="8"/>quam tempus durum <lb n="9"/>rapuit familiam<lb break="no" n="10"/>qu<surplus>a</surplus>e simul Dacia te <lb n="11"/>voluit possedit <lb n="12"/>Micia secum <expan><ex>h</ex><abbr>ave</abbr></expan> <lb n="13"/>puella multum adque <lb n="14"/>in aevum vale
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>In 2 Teile gebrochen. Lesung nach IDR; Zeichnung teilweise abweichend: Z. 4: V[ale]n[tinus]; Z. 5: [---]E[---]; Z. 6: con(iu)gi; auf dem Foto nicht erkennbar. Ab Z. 6 metrische Textteile.</p>
